= AUTOVERSION(1) =
:doctype: manpage

== NAME ==
autoversion - extract head metadata from version-control repositories

== SYNOPSIS ==
*autoversion* [-t output-type] [-o cache-file] [-s variable]

== DESCRIPTION ==

*autoversion* extracts metadata about the head version of your repository.

This program is meant to be used by project build systems to extract properties
that can be used in software version strings. It can create files containing
variable and macro definitions suitable for C, C++, sh, Python, Perl, 
and XCode project descriptions.

